TY  - JOUR
T1  - A Theoretical Study of Organizational Performance Under Information Distortion
AU  - Carley, Kathleen M.
AU  - Lin, Zhiang
Y1  - 1997/07/01
PY  - 1997
DA  - 1997/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.43.7.976
